@Logic0104: thanks for backing me up...as for your problem, to create a torrent first of all you have to know if it is one file or multiple files...if it is a single file then you want to start off by clicking "Add File" then select your file you want to make a torrent out off...then add some trackers...choose piece size or keep it automatic...then click create and save as...this should be all you need for a single file torrent (by single file i mean no folder or anything...just the .iso in your case)

but if you wan to create a multifile torrent (directory) then you change the "add file" instruction in the single file torrent to clicking the "add directory" and then the instructions are the same

hope this helps!!! let me know how it goes
